query:
SELECT
            id                                  AS "id!: uuid::Uuid",
            market_pda                          AS "market_pda!",
            status                              AS "status!",
            COALESCE(price_feed_account, '')    AS "price_feed_account!",
            end_date_utc                        AS "end_date_utc?: chrono::DateTime<chrono::Utc>"
        FROM market_view
        WHERE market_pda = $1
        LIMIT 1
